WHO STARTED THE MISSIONS?

10:20.200 --> 10:21.121
YES?

10:21.240 --> 10:22.127
- FATHER SERRA.

10:22.240 --> 10:22.990
- FATHER JUNIPERO SERRA.

10:23.100 --> 10:24.328
- VERY GOOD.
- SHE WAS WRONG.

10:24.450 --> 10:25.826
THERE COULD BE PLENTY OF PEOPLE

10:25.930 --> 10:28.103
