- SO, YOU SHOULD'VE
SPECIFIED THAT.

10:41.910 --> 10:43.320
YOU JUST SAID
I NEEDED TO RAISE MY HAND.

10:43.430 --> 10:44.215
- I--I DID SPECIFY.
I SAID...

10:44.330 --> 10:45.558
- NO YOU SAID--YOU JUST SAID
RAISE YOUR HAND.

10:45.670 --> 10:46.944
- MAX.

10:47.060 --> 10:48.049
- I DON'T GET WHY WE
HAVE TO RAISE OUR HANDS,

10:48.160 --> 10:49.297
BECAUSE IF YOU WERE IN A
REAL CONVERSATION...

