SOMETHING IN THAT CONVERSATION.

10:53.270 --> 10:54.669
YOU WOULD JUST GO...

10:54.790 --> 10:56.121
- MAX BRAVERMAN, WE WILL TALK
ABOUT THIS LATER.

10:56.240 --> 11:01.724
- I WAS DRINKING AT THE PARTY,
AND ALEX CAME TO PICK ME UP.

11:01.830 --> 11:03.969
