IT IS, THOUGHT THAT

11:08.110 --> 11:12.353
ALEX WAS BOTHERING ME,
AND HE WAS BEING REALLY RUDE.

11:12.460 --> 11:17.329
HE PUSHED ALEX, SO,
AND IT WAS REALLY MESSY,

11:17.430 --> 11:18.499
