11:18.600 --> 11:19.806
THEY GOT INTO A FIGHT.

11:19.920 --> 11:21.740
IT WASN'T HUGE.
IT WAS OVER QUICKLY.

11:21.850 --> 11:23.249
IT WAS MY FAULT.

11:23.370 --> 11:25.747
- NO, LISTEN.
I TAKE FULL RESPONSIBILITY.

11:25.850 --> 11:28.296
OKAY, IT WAS FAULT.

11:28.410 --> 11:29.399
I SHOULDN'T HAVE REACTED.

11:29.510 --> 11:32.889
I SHOULDN'T HAVE PUNCHED
THE GUY.

11:33.000 --> 11:34.888
- OKAY, I ACTUALLY DON'T
EVEN KNOW WHAT TO SAY

11:35.000 --> 11:36.991
TO YOU BOTH RIGHT NOW.

11:37.110 --> 11:41.865
- I HAVE TO TELL YOU ALSO
THAT THE FAMILY

11:41.970 --> 11:46.839
IS GONNA PRESS
CHARGES OF ASSAULT AND BATTERY.

11:46.940 --> 11:51.968
- [sighs]
- DO YOU HAVE A LAWYER?

11:54.850 --> 11:56.329
- YEAH.

11:56.430 --> 11:58.773
