NEEDED TO KNOW.

12:17.210 --> 12:20.316
- BUDDY, COME ON.
- I'M AWAKE.

12:20.420 --> 12:24.493
- IT'S TIME TO GET UP FOR
SCHOOL, WE GOTTA GO.

12:24.600 --> 12:29.424
MAX...

12:29.540 --> 12:31.679
ARE YOU EXCITED ABOUT GOING BACK
TO SCHOOL TODAY?

12:31.780 --> 12:36.911
HOW DO YOU FEEL?
- [sighs]

12:37.030 --> 12:39.362
- DO YOU LIKE YOUR TEACHER?
IS SHE NICE?

12:39.480 --> 12:42.608
- I THOUGHT YOU ALREADY ASKED ME
THIS STUFF LAST NIGHT.

12:42.720 --> 12:43.709
- YOU'RE RIGHT.
I KNOW, I DID. I DID.

12:43.830 --> 12:47.300
I'M JUST--JUST WONDERING.

12:47.420 --> 12:50.480
DO YOU LIKE IT
AS MUCH AS FOOTPATH?

12:50.590 --> 12:53.832
- I DON'T KNOW.
IT'S OKAY.

12:53.940 --> 12:56.044
- HOW ABOUT FRIENDS?
HAVE YOU MADE ANY NEW FRIENDS?

12:56.150 --> 12:58.209
I'M SURE THERE WERE
A LOT OF NICE KIDS THERE

12:58.320 --> 13:00.140
THAT ARE JUST LIKE...
- I DON'T KNOW.

13:00.260 --> 13:01.488
- WANTING TO HANG OUT WITH YOU.

13:01.600 --> 13:02.840
- NO, NO.

13:02.950 --> 13:06.363
CAN I HAVE MY BREAKFAST NOW?

13:06.470 --> 13:08.700
- SURE.

13:08.820 --> 13:11.436
