13:23.660 --> 13:25.139
- IT'S BECAUSE
OF HOW I'M DRESSED?

13:25.250 --> 13:28.549
- I JUST GOT A CALL FROM SOME
GUY AT MY HOME TELLING ME ABOUT

13:28.660 --> 13:30.799
A MEETING WE'RE HAVING
TOMORROW TO DISCUSS THE LEASE

13:30.910 --> 13:32.457
FOR THE SPACE AND
CALLING ME A PARTNER.

13:32.570 --> 13:33.389
- OH, THAT.

13:33.500 --> 13:34.808
- ALL RIGHT.
I'M NOT YOUR PARTNER, OKAY?

13:34.910 --> 13:37.356
