I CAN'T DO THIS WITH YOU.

13:37.470 --> 13:39.938
- YOU RAN A SUCCESSFUL BUSINESS
FOR 15 YEARS.

13:40.060 --> 13:41.607
IT LOOKS GREAT ON AN
APPLICATION.

13:41.710 --> 13:42.631
IT'S NOT A BIG DEAL.

13:42.750 --> 13:43.535
I JUST GAVE THEM YOUR
WORK HISTORY

13:43.650 --> 13:45.151
AND YOUR SOC--

13:45.270 --> 13:46.714
