13:50.030 --> 13:51.474
- YOU'VE DONE THIS BEFORE?

13:51.580 --> 13:52.308
- OF COURSE, I HAVE.

13:52.410 --> 13:53.479
- I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'VE DONE THIS.

13:53.590 --> 13:54.989
- LOOK AT YOU.

13:55.110 --> 13:56.441
- THIS IS EXACTLY WHY
I DIDN'T WANT TO GO

13:56.550 --> 13:58.063
INTO BUSINESS WITH YOU.

13:58.180 --> 14:00.273
- OH, WHY? 'CAUSE I'M COMMITTED
TO MAKING THIS THING HAPPEN?

14:00.390 --> 14:02.278
I DON'T WANNA BLOW THIS
OPPORTUNITY, ADAM.

14:02.390 --> 14:03.596
I SEE SOMETHING IN THAT
BUILDING, OKAY?

14:03.700 --> 14:05.349
- MM-HMM.

14:05.460 --> 14:06.688
- IT'S A PLACE WHERE THE PAST
AND THE PRESENT COME TOGETHER

14:06.810 --> 14:08.949
OVER A LUNCH COUNTER IN
HAIGHT-ASHBURY

14:09.050 --> 14:11.462
AND MAGIC CAN HAPPEN THERE.

14:11.570 --> 14:13.424
I JUST NEED YOU TO COME AND MEET
THE LANDLORD WITH ME.

14:13.540 --> 14:15.428
THERE ARE OTHER COMPANIES THAT
WANT THE SPACE,

14:15.540 --> 14:18.509
AND I GOTTA CONVINCE HIM AND
YOU'RE--YOU HAVE THAT THING.

14:18.610 --> 14:19.918
PEOPLE TRUST YOU.

14:20.030 --> 14:20.678
- WELL, THERE'S A REASON WHY
THEY TRUST ME, CROSBY.

14:20.790 --> 14:22.678
I'M TRUSTWORTHY.
- I KNOW THAT.

14:22.790 --> 14:25.543
YOU'VE GOT THAT,
AND-AND I NEED IT.

14:25.650 --> 14:27.709
JUST COME WITH ME AND TALK ABOUT
THE NUMBERS

14:27.830 --> 14:29.138
THAT WAY YOU DID
IN THE PANCAKE HOUSE.

14:29.240 --> 14:30.867
SOMEHOW, YOU MADE
THAT SOUND EXCITING,

14:30.970 --> 14:31.994
AND THEN YOU DON'T HAVE TO HAVE

14:32.110 --> 14:33.589
ANYTHING TO DO WITH IT
EVER AGAIN.

14:33.700 --> 14:35.201
AS SOON AS I GET THE LEASE,

14:35.320 --> 14:39.484
YOUR NAME WILL COME OFF OF IT
AND THAT'LL BE THAT.

14:42.670 --> 14:44.217
- HEY, HONEY.
- YEAH.

14:44.330 --> 14:47.777
- UM, YOU KNOW, HOW I WAS JOKING
ABOUT ASKING THE LATTE GIRL

14:47.880 --> 14:49.086
IF WE COULD HAVE HER BAY?

14:49.190 --> 14:50.396
- [laughs]
YEAH.

14:50.510 --> 14:52.364
- UM, WHAT IF I DID?

14:52.470 --> 14:53.607
- DID WHAT?

14:53.720 --> 14:57.338
- WHAT IF I ASKED HER
IF WE COULD HAVE HER BABY?

14:57.440 --> 14:59.499
SHE TOLD ME SHE DOESN'T WANT IT.
SHE WAS GIVING IT UP.

14:59.620 --> 15:00.951
AND WE DO WANT IT.

15:01.070 --> 15:02.094
- WAIT, WAIT.

15:02.210 --> 15:04.166
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

15:04.280 --> 15:05.963
- I'M SAYING I WANT--I WANNA
ASK HER.

15:06.070 --> 15:07.958
- HONEY, YOU CAN'T WALK UP TO
SOMEBODY YOU WORK WITH

15:08.070 --> 15:10.482
AND SAY, "EXCUSE ME, IF YOU
AREN'T USING THAT BABY,

15:10.590 --> 15:11.488
CAN WE HAVE IT?"

15:11.600 --> 15:12.908
- WHY NOT?

15:13.010 --> 15:14.216
- WHY NOT?

15:14.320 --> 15:15.389
OKAY.

15:15.500 --> 15:17.593
HONEY, WE DON'T--WE KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT THIS GIRL.

15:17.700 --> 15:18.564
- I DO.
I KNOW HER.

15:18.670 --> 15:19.523
- OKAY.
HOW?

15:19.640 --> 15:20.561
- SHE'S LOVELY.

15:20.670 --> 15:22.080
- SHE'S LOVELY.
GOOD.

15:22.190 --> 15:25.159
- SHE'S--SHE'S SMART AND
BEAUTIFUL AND SO YOUNG...

15:25.260 --> 15:26.739
- AND GREAT AT MAKING LATTES.

15:26.850 --> 15:28.192
YOU DON'T KNOW GENETIC MAKE-UP.

15:28.300 --> 15:29.608
YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT THIS GIRL
HAS BEEN THROUGH.

15:29.720 --> 15:30.709
SHE COULD BE A CRACK ADDICT...

15:30.820 --> 15:31.889
- SHE'S NOT A CRACK ADDICT.

15:32.000 --> 15:32.989
- WE--WE COULD BE CRACK ADDICT S.

15:33.100 --> 15:34.260
SHE KNOWS NOTHING ABOUT US.

15:34.380 --> 15:35.449
- WELL, YOU CAN MEET HER.
I CAN EASILY ARRANGE THAT.

15:35.550 --> 15:36.471
- NO.

15:36.590 --> 15:37.545
IT'S NOT HOW'S IT DONE.

15:37.660 --> 15:39.616
- WELL, CAN YOU THINK
OUTSIDE THE BOX HERE?

15:39.730 --> 15:41.243
THIS IS FALLING IN OUR LAPS.

15:41.350 --> 15:43.511
- I CAN'T THINK OUTSIDE THE BOX
ON THIS ONE.

15:43.630 --> 15:44.654
- THIS IS--IT'S AN AMAZING
OPPORTUNITY, BABE.

15:44.770 --> 15:45.964
CAN YOU C(NJgSIDER IT?

15:46.080 --> 15:47.832
YOU JUST--YOU JUST CAN'T GO
ROGUE ON ME

15:47.940 --> 15:50.147
AND HAMMER OUT A DEAL
AT THE COFFEE CART.

15:50.250 --> 15:53.139
THAT'S CRAZY, JULIA.

15:55.880 --> 15:58.872
YOU KNOW THAT'S CRAZY,
RIGHT?

15:58.990 --> 16:00.389
WE'RE GOING TO GET A BABY.

16:00.510 --> 16:02.193
WE'RE GONNA GET OUR BABY.
BUT WE'RE GONNA DO IT

16:02.300 --> 16:04.677
THROUGH THE PROPER CHANNELS.

16:04.790 --> 16:06.269
WE'RE GONNA DO IT THE RIGHT WAY,

16:06.370 --> 16:10.750
AND YOU JUST HAVE TO BE
PATIENT HERE.

16:12.830 --> 16:15.890
OKAY?

16:16.000 --> 16:18.139
- OKAY.

16:29.600 --> 16:32.114
- DO YOU HAVE ANYTHING ELSE
TO DO?

16:32.230 --> 16:33.128
- NO, THAT'S WHAT--YEAH,
ACTUALLY

16:33.230 --> 16:35.881
I WAS ABOUT 45 MINUTES EARLY
TONIGHT.

16:35.990 --> 16:38.094
