17:04.850 --> 17:05.919
- OH YEAH?
YOUR OLDER BROTHER?

17:06.020 --> 17:06.873
- SO I PRETEND LIKE
I AM MY BROTHER.

17:06.990 --> 17:08.218
YEAH MY OLDER BROTHER.
- OKAY.

17:08.330 --> 17:09.433
- WHO'S GETTING MARRIED
ACTUALLY THIS DECEMBER.

17:09.540 --> 17:11.428
- OH, HIS FIRST--
- YEAH, HIS FIRST.

17:11.540 --> 17:12.746
- HE'S LIKE 30-SOMETHING, RIGHT?

17:12.850 --> 17:13.782
- YEAH, 32.
- YEAH, HIS FIRST.

17:13.890 --> 17:14.675
- GOOD.
