17:14.790 --> 17:15.779
- YEAH.

17:15.890 --> 17:17.471
- I'M GLAD.

17:17.580 --> 17:20.333
- HE'S THE FIRST ONE AND,
YEAH, THEY'RE DOING IT IN CABO.

17:20.450 --> 17:23.032
