17:31.700 --> 17:33.497
- YEAH, THERE'S A LOT OF TIME
TO FIGURE OUT.

17:33.600 --> 17:35.522
- NO, NO, IT WAS JUST A LONG
TIME FROM NOW.

17:35.640 --> 17:36.493
I'M NOT SURE WHAT WE'RE GONNA BE
DOING IN DECEMBER, YOU KNOW.

17:36.600 --> 17:37.419
- NO, OF COURSE.
- IN THE MONTH OF DECEMBER.

17:37.530 --> 17:38.326
THAT'S REALLY NICE.
- ABSOLUTELY.

17:38.430 --> 17:42.184
- THANK YOU.
