17:42.300 --> 17:46.407
- THEY'RE, UM...
IT'LL BE THERE.

17:46.510 --> 17:47.260
- GREAT.

17:47.370 --> 17:48.189
- YEAH?
- YEAH.

17:48.300 --> 17:49.289
GOOD MOVIE, GOOD WALK.
THANK YOU.

17:49.410 --> 17:50.547
- IT WAS--IT WAS A GREAT NIGHT.

17:50.650 --> 17:51.787
- MM-HMM.

17:51.890 --> 17:54.404
- I GOT A CHANCE TO THINK.

17:54.520 --> 17:59.548
- SO TOMORROW, AM I--AM I GONNA
