SO MUCH

18:14.610 --> 18:16.362
JUST BY SPENDING TIME WITH ME
AND JUST HANGING OUT

18:16.470 --> 18:18.529
AND JUST TAKING MY MIND OFF
OF IT.

18:18.640 --> 18:21.950
AND THAT--THAT MEANS
THE WORLD TO ME.

18:22.060 --> 18:23.231
- OKAY.

18:23.340 --> 18:27.401
- ALL RIGHT? LET ME
JUST DO THIS MYSELF, OKAY?

18:27.520 --> 18:29.272
THERE'S SOMETHING I JUST NEED
TO GET THROUGH,

18:29.380 --> 18:30.517
AND I'LL TELL YOU
ABOUT IT LATER.

18:30.620 --> 18:34.135
