OKAY?

18:34.250 --> 18:35.137
- OKAY.

18:35.250 --> 18:36.239
- ALL RIGHT?

18:36.350 --> 18:39.171
- OKAY.
YEAH, IF YOU NEED TO, YEAH.

18:39.290 --> 18:40.734
- TELL ME YOU LOVE ME?

18:40.840 --> 18:41.932
- OKAY, I LOVE YOU.

18:42.050 --> 18:43.358
- CAN YOU GIVE ME A KISS?

18:43.460 --> 18:46.463
- OKAY.

18:46.570 --> 18:48.913
GOOD NIGHT.
- GOOD NIGHT.

18:49.020 --> 18:50.874
- GOOD LUCK.

18:50.990 --> 18:56.781
- THANK YOU.

18:56.890 --> 18:58.471
- HEY, HONEY.

18:58.580 --> 18:59.740
- YEAH.

